4987.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cfy1665702534987.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cfy1665702534987.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cfy1665702534987\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Delete the DSP view object.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"cfy1665702534987__topic_d127409e1_d127410e1_d127411e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfy1665702534987__p_d127412e1_d127413e1_d127414e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">unifaceViewObject</var>.<span class=\"keyword apiname\">remove()</span>\n</code>\n</p>\n</section> <section class=\"section\" id=\"cfy1665702534987__section_w1379ab1b5b3_w1380ab1b5_w1381ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d239320e64\">Return Value</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cfy1665702534987__section_w1382ab1b5b5_w1383ab1b5_w1384ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d239320e73\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfy1665702534987__p_d127424e1_d127425e1_d127426e1\">After calling this function, the View object is\n            invalid, and any attempt to call its member functions will throw the following\n            exception: <code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</code>. </p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"cfy1665702534987__note_a477938c745598891bbe27e5cc848485\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> This function does not work\n            with the default view that is automatically created by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">weblayout</span>\n            ProcScript command.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/shk1665703139073.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</a><p>Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526427\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526427\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "remove() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Delete the DSP view object. unifaceViewObject . remove() Return Value None Description After calling this function, the View object is invalid, and any attempt to call its member functions will throw the following exception: uniface.InvalidDataObjectException . Note: This function does not work with the default view that is automatically created by the weblayout ProcScript command. Related Links uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}